                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;This issue was created by maloo for jianyu &amp;lt;yujian@whamcloud.com&amp;gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This issue relates to the following test suite run: &lt;a href=&quot;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/49a80893-9ad9-4ec3-965f-20418946b434&quot; class=&quot;external-link&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;nofollow noopener&quot;&gt;https://testing.whamcloud.com/test_sets/49a80893-9ad9-4ec3-965f-20418946b434&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;test_100 failed with the following error:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;div class=&quot;preformatted panel&quot; style=&quot;border-width: 1px;&quot;&gt;&lt;div class=&quot;preformattedContent panelContent&quot;&gt;
&lt;pre&gt;mount lustre  on /mnt/lustre.....
Starting client: trevis-154vm42.trevis.whamcloud.com:  -o user_xattr,flock 10.240.39.202@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
CMD: trevis-154vm42.trevis.whamcloud.com mkdir -p /mnt/lustre
CMD: trevis-154vm42.trevis.whamcloud.com mount -t lustre -o user_xattr,flock 10.240.39.202@tcp:/lustre /mnt/lustre
CMD: trevis-154vm42.trevis.whamcloud.com cp /etc/passwd /mnt/lustre/a
CMD: trevis-154vm42.trevis.whamcloud.com rm /mnt/lustre/a
CMD: trevis-154vm42.trevis.whamcloud.com grep /mnt/lustre&apos; &apos; /proc/mounts &amp;gt; /dev/null
setup single mount lustre success
CMD: trevis-154vm45 lshowmount -v
trevis-154vm45: *** buffer overflow detected ***: terminated
trevis-154vm45: bash: line 1: 1439433 Aborted                 (core dumped) ( PATH=$PATH:/usr/lib64/lustre/utils:/usr/lib64/lustre/tests:/sbin:/usr/sbin; cd /usr/lib64/lustre/tests; LUSTRE=&quot;/usr/lib64/lustre&quot; bash -c &quot;lshowmount -v&quot; )
pdsh@trevis-154vm42: trevis-154vm45: ssh exited with exit code 134
 conf-sanity test_100: @@@@@@ FAIL: lshowmount have no output MGS
&lt;/pre&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;&lt;/div&gt;

